Package model

Class DBTables

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.DBTables
  • public class DBTables
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a DBTables object. The DBTables object holds the list of Customers, Appointments, Contacts, Countries, Users, and First-Level Divisions of the Database.

      • lookUpCustomer

        public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<Customer> lookUpCustomer​(java.lang.String customerName)
        This method looks up a customer that contains a portion of the string given. This method goes through the list of customers in DBTables and adds that customer to an observable list (matchingCustomers) if the customer name contains the given string. It then returns the matchingCustomer list.
        Parameters:
        customerName - the string to see if it is contained in the list of customer names
        Returns:
        the observable list of matching customers
